{"tid":1378241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔該寫信俾晒所有國家領䄂 要求佢地不再承認香港政府","createTime":"2019-07-28T15:29:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-02T07:41:58.000Z","uid":292024,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e2eedc22ad2c746bbe34f68808544586201391b6","tid":1378241,"uid":292024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T15:29:23.000Z","msg":"直至香港政府重組，警隊重組。<br />\n<br />\n由於現時警權過大，香港政府已經無法控制政局，任由執法者濫行私刑，破壞法治基石，香港制度已經徹底崩潰，速請各國領袖作出適當行動罷免現今腐敗政權，有必要請全面對香港斷交，進行全面制裁，全面撤資。<br />\n<br />\n以最近狀況睇，明顯唔會再同你地講人道，暴力鎮壓每次都升級，亦都大規模搜捕拉人，咁落去唔係辨法，學生年青人你地好盡力了，唔想睇到你地一個俾一個拉，一定要搵外國幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e4e0dd7c767f3c35792dcd73605fdf951e2df2","tid":1378241,"uid":292024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:21:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2a3101f9f8b774f4bb049a739568f6c8f7bb794","tid":1378241,"uid":292024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:28:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e6eccf44f642bd8d26506e4906902b6ecd895ec","tid":1378241,"uid":292024,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:29:05.000Z","msg":"唔好淨係行一條示威路，多啲諗其他方法"},{"pid":"dc31b0a99cb0ee389e07afa54ae0add7bb03ed8e","tid":1378241,"uid":168965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T00:34:13.000Z","msg":"錯手負皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> push"},{"pid":"1233ef24d4f7dd1ea2c61008abfc5cdc6e6406a6","tid":1378241,"uid":292024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:25:25.000Z","msg":"做多啲文宣一定要外國幫手，問問各國會不會承認一個跟黑社會合作既政府"},{"pid":"deefd67f2da45f71d26333917a2b2ebe50622d1d","tid":1378241,"uid":258362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T07:33:01.000Z","msg":"kill2#<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><